      <title>分析师表示，日本央行的鸽派决定为日元进一步走弱铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/dovish-boj-decision-paves-way-for-even-weaker-yen-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，日本央行周五基本维持货币政策不变，市场将认为这是鸽派举动，并可能导致日元进一步走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/dovish-boj-decision-paves-way-for-even-weaker-yen-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 04:36:02 GMT</pubDate>
